Overview:

hugin uses the following libraries. make sure that they are completely installed (including dev packages)

REQUIRED LIBRARIES/PACKAGES:

wxwindows 2.4.0 or higher (libary and development packages)
wxwindows needs to be compiled with the xrc extension. You might need to install
wxwin-contrib or similar.

Panorama Tools, get it from
http://bugbear.blackfish.org.uk/~bruno/panorama-tools/ (linux)
or
http://www.tawbaware.com/maxlyons/pano12ml.htm (windows)

Compilation:

do the following:
$ ./configure
$ make
$ make install
